aa(lp139
VIs this change, though, a real change,
p140
aVor is it a figment of the imagination
p141
aVof the patient themselves?
p142
aVWell we studied teenagers' attitudes
p143
aVto photographs of patients having this corrective facial surgery.
p144
aVAnd what we found was \u2014
p145
aVwe jumbled up the photographs
p146
aVso they couldn't recognize the before and after \u2014
p147
aVwhat we found was that the patients were regarded
p148
aVas being more attractive after the surgery.
p149
aVWell that's not surprising, but we also asked them to judge them
p150
aVon honesty, intelligence,
p151
aVfriendliness, violence.
p152
aVThey were all perceived as being
p153
aVless than normal in all those characteristics \u2014
p154
aVmore violent, etc. \u2014 before the surgery.
p155
aVAfter the surgery,
p156
aVthey were perceived as being more intelligent,
p157
aVmore friendly, more honest, less violent \u2014
p158
aVand yet we hadn't operated on their intellect
p159
aVor their character.
