aa(lp248
VIs this business
p249
aVabout appearance and preoccupation with it
p250
aVa Western phenomenon?
p251
aVMuzetta's family give the lie to this.
p252
aVThis is a little Bangladeshi girl from the east end of London
p253
aVwho's got a huge malignant tumor on the right side of her face,
p254
aVwhich has already made her blind
p255
aVand which is rapidly growing and is going to kill her shortly.
p256
aVAfter she had surgery to remove the tumor,
p257
aVher parents dressed her in this beautiful green velvet dress,
p258
aVa pink ribbon in her hair,
p259
aVand they wanted the painting to be shown around the world,
p260
aVdespite the fact that they were orthodox Muslims
p261
aVand the mother wore a full burqa.
