aa(lp352
VThe face transplant has a role
p353
aVprobably in burns patients to replace the skin.
p354
aVWe can replace the underlying skeletal structure,
p355
aVbut we're still not good at replacing the facial skin.
p356
aVSo it's very valuable
p357
aVto have that tool in our armamentarium.
p358
aVBut the patients are going to have to take drugs
p359
aVthat suppress their immune system for the rest of their lives.
p360
aVWhat does that mean?
p361
aVThey have an increased risk of infection, an increased risk of malignancy.
p362
aVThis is not a life-saving transplant \u2014
p363
aVlike a heart, or liver, or lung transplant \u2014
p364
aVit is a quality-of-life transplant,
p365
aVand as a result,
p366
aVare the patients going to say, if they get a malignant cancer 10 or 15 years on,
